		 'commit all changes 
  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function
	
Public Function cgt15_f2()

On Error Resume Next

  Dim ws As Workspace
  Dim db As Database
  Dim strSQL As String

  Set db = ws.Databases(0)

	db.Execute sql, dbFailOnError

		 'commit all changes 
  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function
	
Public Function cgt15_f3()

On Error Resume Next

  Dim ws As Workspace
  Dim db As Database
  Dim strSQL As String

  Set ws = DBEngine.Workspaces(0)
  Set db = ws.Databases(0)

On Error GoTo Proc_Err

		 'commit all changes 
  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function

  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function

  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function

  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function

	sql="update gaseosa set auxiliar='OBTIENE en CGT de Mayo 2015' where dni='12376072W'"
	db.Execute sql, dbFailOnError

		 'commit all changes 
  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function
	
Public Function cgt15_f8()

On Error Resume Next

  Dim ws As Workspace
  Dim db As Database
  Dim strSQL As String

  Set ws = DBEngine.Workspaces(0)
  Set db = ws.Databases(0)

On Error GoTo Proc_Err
  'start a transaction to ensure all updates are run or rolled back
  ws.BeginTrans
	sql="update gaseosa set codcentrodefinitivo='02005001' where dni='07556299V'"
	db.Execute sql, dbFailOnError
	sql="update gaseosa set codcentrocursoactual='02005001' where dni='07556299V'"
	db.Execute sql, dbFailOnError
	sql="update gaseosa set auxiliar='DENEGADO en CGT de Mayo 2015' where dni='07556299V'"
	db.Execute sql, dbFailOnError
	sql="update gaseosa set codcentrodefinitivo='19003917' where dni='70647297Z'"

  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function

		 'commit all changes 
  ws.CommitTrans

Proc_Exit:
  Set ws = Nothing
  Set db = Nothing
  Exit Function

Proc_Err:
  ws.Rollback
  MsgBox "Error updating: " & Err.Description
  Resume Proc_Exit
End Function

  Dim ws As Workspace
  Dim db As Database
  Dim strSQL As String

  Set db = ws.Databases(0)
